# Package Manager: pnpm Only

- Use `pnpm` for all package management commands in this repository.
- Do not use `npm` commands for install, run, create, publish, or scripts.
- Prefer `pnpm dlx` instead of `npx`.
- Prefer `pnpm add`, `pnpm add -D`, `pnpm remove`, and `pnpm install`.
- Prefer `pnpm run <script>` (or `pnpm <script>` where appropriate).

## Command Mapping

- `npm install` -> `pnpm install`
- `npm i <pkg>` -> `pnpm add <pkg>`
- `npm i -D <pkg>` -> `pnpm add -D <pkg>`
- `npm uninstall <pkg>` -> `pnpm remove <pkg>`
- `npm run <script>` -> `pnpm run <script>`
- `npx <tool>` -> `pnpm dlx <tool>`
